// T24 v2.1 — Turbo Air brand page. Mid-tier value brand with aggressive market share growth
// post-2018. Long Beach CA distribution = local logistics advantage vs True (Missouri),
// Perlick (Wisconsin), Traulsen (Texas). Tiered quality framework (M3R premium / MSR mid /
