    <h2>Turbo Air repair costs.</h2>

    <p class="lead">Diagnostic is $120 (commercial tier), waived with repair. Long Beach distribution proximity often means parts arrive same-day or next-day, especially on M3R-series common SKUs.</p>

    <table class="price-table">
